  Select Provider
  Choose the default backend for new sessions. The current session stays unchanged

› 1. OpenAI (current)    Use ChatGPT sign-in or a saved OpenAI API key. Default
                         model: gpt-5.5.
  2. Claude (Anthropic)  Use Claude models with a saved API key. Default model:
                         claude-sonnet-4-20250514.
  3. Ollama (local)      Use a local Ollama server. Default model: gpt-oss:20b.
  4. LM Studio (local)   Use a local LM Studio server. Default model: openai/gpt-
                         oss-20b.

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
